snippet.title: Chronomon - A Monster Taming Farm SIM
snippet.description:
Our newest trailer showcasing how monster taming and farming sim games can meld together! Capture/Train your Chronomon - get them to help on the farm. 

Available for ALL platforms with cross-save compatibility. You can even play on your WearOS smartwatch! 

Wishlist on Steam today! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2370420/Chronomon/
